<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>- أَوْ خَلْفَ مَنْ لَمْ يَجْمَعْ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>- أَوْ إِحْدَاهُمَا مُنْفَرِدًا وَالأُخْرَى جَمَاعَةً.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>- أَوْ بِمَأَمُومٍ الأُولَى وَبِآخَرَ الثَّانِيَةَ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>- أَوْ بِمَنْ لَمْ يَجْمَعْ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>صَحَّ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>فَصْلٌ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> تَصِحَّ صَلَاةُ الخَوْفِ:</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>- بِقِتَالٍ مُبَاحٍ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>- وَلَوْ حَضَرًا.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>مَعَ خَوْفِ هَجْمِ العَدْوِّ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>- عَلَى سِتَّةِ أَوْجَهٍ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَإِذَا اشْتَدَّ الخَوْفُ:</span> صَلَّوْا رِجَالًا وَرُكْبَانًا، لِلقِبْلَةِ وَغَيْرِهَا.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>- وَلَا يَلْزمُ افْتِتَاحُهَا إِلَيْهَا وَلَوْ أَمْكَنَ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>- يُومِئُونَ طَاقَتَهُمْ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>- وَلِمُصَلٍّ كَرٌّ وَفَرٌّ لِمَصْلَحَةٍ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>